Arch Linux packaging
====================

Place here:
- Dockerfile          — build environment image (base: archlinux:latest)
- PKGBUILD            — adapted from archdevlab/linux-lqx, parameterized on ARCH
- build-inside.sh     — script run inside the container to invoke makepkg

Reference: https://github.com/archdevlab/linux-lqx
           https://github.com/damentz/liquorix-package/tree/6.x/master/scripts/archlinux
